data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! This spectacular move-in ready gem boasts four bedrooms, including a master suite with a split design for added privacy. The custom-designed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring dark cherry wood cabinets, a pantry, built-in storage, Italian quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances, including a newer double-door refrigerator. The elegance of porcelain tile floors flows seamlessly throughout.  Laminate floors grace the living areas and master suite, where you'll also find a large walk-in custom closet. Both bathrooms offer double vanities, tasteful tiled walls, showers, and a luxurious Jacuzzi tub in the master bath.Mechanically, this home is top-notch, with a new energy-efficient A/C unit ensuring year-round comfort.  Newer  Roof The roof was expertly replaced in 2011, and the water heater was upgraded in 2016.  Now, let's talk about peace of mind. This home is fully hurricane-protected, featuring accordion shutters and rollup panels that cover the rear windows and screened patio.  Also, this home has a whole house generator that is regularily maintained and has a 550 gallon tank!! Never lose power again. 
 Your safety and comfort are our top priorities!Not only is this home a haven of comfort and security, but it's also conveniently located just a couple of miles away from the entrances to both the Turnpike and I-95. Easy access to major highways makes commuting a breeze.Plus, this home is situated in a coveted A-rated school district with highly-rated schools nearby, ensuring an exceptional education for your children. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
